Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Romefeller Foundation's\Nenforced rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...has caused disputes to\Nspring up around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Our country has declared\Nitself a peaceful nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we've been trying\Nto avoid resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be guaranteed peace\Nif we let them control us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But you couldn't really\Ncall that true peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a method of oppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd lead to a new despotic\Nrule and more disputes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly hope that we're\Nmaking the right decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the ages, the world\Nhas had many countries...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...many races, and many\Nways of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we should\Naccept the fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...that some disputes in\Nthe past were unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom is a right given\Nto all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But we must realize that people\Ncan't be given complete freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What we need in order\Nto attain harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...is to be thoughtful\Nto others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A peaceful future\Ndoesn't lie in fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our job to learn\Nfrom our past...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...and use that experience to\Nbuild a new and correct future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid that our\Nnation alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...couldn't act against the\NRomefeller Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But Total Pacifism...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...as advocated by the\Nlate King Peacecraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...is well rooted here in\Nthe Sanc Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Its presence is a\Nstrong support.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware that my speech\Nand behavior...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...seem impudent despite\Nthe fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I'm following\Nmy father's teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's my sincere hope\Nthat more countries...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...and more people can\None day attain true peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To that end I ask for\Nyour assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For true peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The meeting ended\Nwithout a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if we're watching\Nevery move you people make.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that your meeting\Nended so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're determined to\Nget our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably why the\Nmeeting didn't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be on our way,\Nsince we're not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ruining the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't necessarily dislike\Nthe Romefeller Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want you to rectify\Nyour mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And do it before many\Npeople lose their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Townsend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've found two space suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that only\Nthe two landed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no reason for caution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- You may return.{\i0}\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Space Colonies and\NRomefeller have joined forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam pilots'\Nmissions are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders are out to execute\Nthe Gundam pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Executing them would be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Although our country is\Nunder Romefeller's rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd rather not\Nget rid of them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not big on animals, Quatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then play with the dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they'd rather\Nplay with you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Animals have the natural ability\Nto sense kindness in people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is kindness necessary in a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not while you're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But kindness is probably\Nneeded the rest of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially considering there\Nare orders to execute us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately headquarters\Ncontacted us and will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...picking up you Gundam pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad; it means I don't\Nhave to carry out the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll still have to hand\Nyou over to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't trouble you any\Nmore than we already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your job to hand us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna surrender\Nwithout a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know what we'll do\Ntill the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But we won't die aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are certainly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're involved in Romefeller's\Ncontrol policies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we have doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting involved was our only\Nchoice to avoid futile battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You made the correct decision,\Nto protect the people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's the same decision\Nour people in space made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Romefeller Foundation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...we Gundam pilots are\Na mere obstruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who's after our\Nlives is an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to fight to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one and only thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...that we can and must\Ncarry out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna die,\Nthat is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, carrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:06:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We have orders to shoot\Nyou down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surrender at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea's gotta be cold\Nat a latitude of 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, I can't simply give\Nthe craft up to OZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally Po.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be thankful you\Ngot a fireplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The new OZ is a warm-\Nhearted organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only treating me like\Na special guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...until you confirm what's\Nin the carrier, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We were told to watch\Nfor rebels...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...who would help the Gundam\Npilots once they took action.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But we didn't expect to\Nget our hands on a Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true that the Gundam\Npilots have returned to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta make sure\NI deliver it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more nations are\Ntaking sides with Romefeller.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be a rocky road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The metal detector won't be\Nable to pick up the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll pick up the carrier,\Nso find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's wrong?!\N- Enemies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the real thing\Nat the bottom of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I might tell a lie\Nso that you'll free me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna retaliate against\NRomefeller...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I need the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fighting the\Nsame enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So decide if you\Nwanna negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My time's run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So it IS real then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the enemy\Nbuilt up so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one OZ referred\Nto as Zero One.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted the\NGundam to save yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What country are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will say that it's\Nresisting Romefeller.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So it could be attacked\Nany time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruler of the nation is\Nindispensable for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And is capable of bringing\Ntrue peace to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you expect to win\Nagainst Romefeller...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...with just the Gundams?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confident in its pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd defeat Romefeller's\Nambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As acquaintances of\Nthe Gundam pilots...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...you and I tend to\Noverdo things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's risky to depend\Non them too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the moment\NI want their help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody wants to get\Ninvolved in wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But those who have the\Nability to fight should fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At least that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reluctant to use\Nthe word "righteous".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But the word suits those kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling them righteous\Nmight really be a sad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it forces them to\Nact like modern heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do, it's unlikely that\NI'll take a wrong path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Plans to wipe out the Gundams\Nare progressing in two places.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Could the other be the\NGundam you left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're calling it "Zero One".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, have you heard\Nof the Sanc Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes up in Romefeller's\Nconfidential data...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...as a problematic nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sanc Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're covering their tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're very interested\Nin finding Zero One.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And also its pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we could be\Nof some help to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These two dogs are the only\Nones guarding us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're telling us to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This nation isn't looking\Nfor any battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're like time bombs\Nand will bring trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The commander here has\Na weak point, to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Quatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's headed our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Any word from Count Townsend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Check at once.\N- Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're heading straight\Nfor Romefeller's forces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't they be escaping?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an urgent message\Nfrom those forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...demanding information\Non the approaching craft!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Townsend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- This was left behind.\N- By the Gundam pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Count, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please inform them at once\Nthat we've escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't cause you any more\Ntrouble than we already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be wiser just to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But we always end up fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever I go it's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because fighting is\Nall I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy attack! Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy in sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching torpedoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this? An attack?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nuts but\Nit's the only way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them, for the sake\Nof the Sanc Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No funny stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Advise the other ships too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to make things\Nworse than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Better do what my partner\Ntells you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I would have\Nalready opened fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I just want you\Nto leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't figure\Nyou can allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, where should we\Nhead to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any place\NI wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of kind people\Nright here on the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'd be causing them\Na great deal of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...by doing nothing more\Nthan meeting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no place to go,\Ndo we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Quatre...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're trying\Nto forget the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Earth's a war zone,\NI'm gonna fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no choice but\Nto fight either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're Gundam pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The battlefield is the only\Nplace we're allowed to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For us, I guess the meaning\Nof life is to survive battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sally here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The surface is under control.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How're things?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like meeting a long\Nlost friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Use it to protect your country.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't thank you enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Lucrezia Noin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The country I'm serving is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Noin, it's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't have to tell me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I trust you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm just honored to{\i0}\N{\i1}help a nation...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that's trying to oppose{\i0}\N{\i1}Romefeller.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna go and{\i0}\N{\i1}look for another Gundam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you hear about one{\i0}\N{\i1}I'd welcome your help.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'd be great to have{\i0}\N{\i1}two or three pilots.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a chance\Nto earn your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you my word, in the\Nname of God and our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The guards for the Peace Nations\NAssembly are leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So I rushed here for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was positive they'd\Ntake this opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...to invade the Sanc\NKingdom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the mobile dolls\Njust won't do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Those dinky things don't have\Na chance against the knights...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...protecting their precious\NPrincess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right with that\Nnew student arriving today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask, Pagan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard she was a blood\Nrelative of Duke Dermail...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...the central figure of the\NRomefeller Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I mustn't make\Nassumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But given that the Foundation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...doesn't think highly of the\NSanc Kingdom's pacifism...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't help thinking\Nit's a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Romefeller Foundation\Nsaid they wish to learn more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...about educational policies\Non building a peaceful nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they wanted to send\Na student to our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have problems believing\Neverything the Foundation says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Doubting people won't\Nget you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides there's nothing mistaken\Nabout what we're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this'd be a great chance\Nto make them understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Relena Peacecraft,\NDirector of this institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Sanc Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't aware that the Princess\Nof the Sanc Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...was also the Director\Nof the institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, my name is\NDorothy Catalonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still powerless to do\Nanything on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm learning Total Pacifism\Nthat my father advocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as everyone else is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As you're aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've come here on behalf\Nof the Romefeller Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Foundation is surrounded\Nwith weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...in this war-torn world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a great interest in the\Npolicies of the Sanc Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially in what you'd do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...if the forces decided to\Ninvade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This beautiful scenery would\Ndisappear in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And the hearts that cherish this\Nbeauty would also be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody in their right mind\Nwould want to hand over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Kingdom to such\Nfoolish barbarians.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So what would you do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe there are any\Nfoolish people in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,People reach an understanding\Nby talking things over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe such discussions\Nwill bring peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...to all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a foolish person myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I love wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'd only be a nuisance\Nby staying in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The main objective of the\NSanc Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...is to provide a place for\Nthese discussions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I welcome more talks like\Nthis, Miss Dorothy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But please call me Dorothy,\NMiss Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can just call\Nme Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the heroine of\Nour times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself feel a great\Nadmiration for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorothy Catalonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the same age\Nas Miss Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected her to be brainwashed\Nby Romefeller's oppressive ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't seem\Nto be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we must be cautious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep an eye on her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had this ready\Njust in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dorothy seems tougher\Nthan I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Dorothy truly gets\Nenjoyment out of battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, when Miss Relena\Nis rejecting battles...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm worried that Dorothy\Ncould exhaust Miss Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relena's thoughts are{\i0}\N{\i1}commendable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She knows that her actions{\i0}\N{\i1}are highly risky now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our mission is to protect her{\i0}\N{\i1}in operation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that means getting\Nsome weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't afford to let{\i0}\N{\i1}Relena get killed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...like the assassinated King{\i0}\N{\i1}of this country.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're confronted{\i0}\N{\i1}by a part of history...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that could easily be{\i0}\N{\i1}repeated, but must not.{\i0}
